Patch Set 4: I would prefer that you didn't merge this

Yeah, this code looks good assuming we're adding DB2 support. But. . .  are we? I keep searching the openstack-dev list and can't find the plan or general approval or whatever?
I have heard a bit of noise about there being a functional integration requirement before support is added--is that being tracked somewhere? I don't think it makes sense for glance alone to support DB2-under-sqlalchemy, the way it might for other types of persistence backends.
